snippet: Roughly 2,000 Clinton administration documents were unsealed by the National Archives on Friday, the fifth such release of memos and transcripts that had been withheld from public view.
lead_paragraph: Roughly 2,000 Clinton administration documents were unsealed by the National Archives on Friday, the fifth such release of memos and transcripts that had been withheld from public view.

headline.main: In Newly Released Clinton Papers, Ire Over Speeches
